data.description: A Spacious Oasis in Bluffton! This splendid 3-bed, 2.5-bath residence is an enchanting opportunity, offering 2,184 sq/ft of light and bright interior, private office & central kitchen w/stainless appliances. Wraparound windows highlight stunning lagoon views, deep grassed yard & expansive patio. The second floor retreat includes an oversized owner’s suite w/large private bath & ample storage. Dedicated laundry, guest beds and additional full bath are just down the hall. HVAC 2019. Steps from your community pool ensures endless summer enjoyment. Enjoy close proximity to May River High School and future shopping/dining at New Riverside Village.
